data.description: This beautiful home is conveniently located off of Victory & Meridian Rd. in the established Strada Bellissimia Community! It allows for easy access to anywhere in the Treasure Valley. It features 4 Bedrooms, bonus room, large walk in pantry and an abundant of natural light. Not to mention a covered patio for the summer nights ahead and a fully fenced east facing back yard. It has been extremely well cared for and is looking for it's new owners! Be sure to take the 3D tour! White cabinets in garage, hot tub and shed all stay.
